elogind (235-2) unstable; urgency=medium

  * rename libelogind into libelogind0 to match SONAME
  * add patch to fix wrong path in elogind-dbus
  * Change maint-scripts for init packages:
    - Do not restart elogind on upgrade (all)
    - Don't call 'update-rc.d elogind disable' on remove (dbus and sysv);
      call 'update-rc.d -f elogind remove' only on purge
    - added preinst (all) to make sure that two way of bringing up
      elogind are not used at the same time.

